hadiths[3]{hadithnumber,text}:
2287,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (qarz ada karne mein) maaldaar ki taraf se taal matol karna zulm hai. aur agar tum mein se kisi ka qarz kisi maaldaar par hawaala diya jaey to usey qabool kare.
2288,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, maaldaar ki taraf se ( qarz ada karne mein) taal matol karna zulm hai. aur agar kisi ka qarz kisi maaldaar ke hawaaley kya jaey to wo usey qabool kare."
2289,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood they ke aik janaaza laya gaya. logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke uski Namaz padha dijiye. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya is par koi qarz hai? logon ne bataya ke nahi koi qarz nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke maiyat ne kuchh maal bhi chhoda hai? logon ne arz kya koi maal bhi nahi chhoda . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaaze-janaaza padhai. iske baad aik doosra janaaza laya gaya logon ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap unki bhi namaaze-janaaza padha dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kisi ka qarz bhi maiyat par hai? arz kya gaya ke hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kuchh maal bhi chhoda hai? logon ne kaha ke teen Dinar chhodey hain. aap ne unki bhi namaaze-janaaza padhai. phir tesraa janaaza laya gaya. logon ne aap ki khidmat mein arz kya ke uski Namaz padha dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq bhi wahi malum farmaya, kya koi maal tarka chhoda hai? logon ne kaha ke nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, aur is par kisi ka qarz bhi hai? logon ne kaha ke haan, teen Dinar hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke phir apne sathi ki tum hi log Namaz padh lo. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) boley, ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki Namaz padha dijiye, unka qarz main ada kar doonga. tab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par Namaz padhai."
